The paper discusses the design and development of a low-cost humanoid robot platform for research purposes, with a focus on its hardware and software components. This makes it likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of ROS-based software development, which suggests that it could also belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computer Vision (cs.CV), Systems and Control (cs.SY), or Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
